title: Obama goes kitesurfing | Reuters.com
text:
NECKER ISLAND, British Virgin Islands Reuters / Tuesday, February 07, 2017 
Former President Barack Obama tries his hand at kite surfing during a holiday with British businessman Richard Branson on his island Moskito, in the British Virgin Islands, in a picture handed out by Virgin on February 7, 2017.
